## Known issues / troubleshooting

| Symptom | Cause / fix |
|---------|-------------|
| DB `P1000` on port 5432 | Use `DATABASE_URL` with **5433** and `docker compose up -d postgres` |
| No `/api/books/search` in Network tab | Wrong search box (use pink Open Library box); restart dev + hard refresh; check client hydration |
| Search API 401 | `/api/books/search` must be in `PUBLIC_PATHS` in `middleware.ts` |
| Covers lost on Vercel | Use URL or deploy with Docker + volume |
| `npm run test:book-search` fails HTTP | Start `npm run dev` first |

## Conventions

- Minimize scope; match existing patterns; no commits unless user asks
- Package name `my-library` (npm); user-facing name Arinda's Library
- Only create commits when explicitly requested
